Features:
=========
a) The Script uses php combined with ajax which makes the faster retrival of the data.
b) The script provides the easter sunday calculation for large span of years.
c) Simple to integrate this page with any web site that supports php.

Requirements:
=============
Linux or Windows server (it *should* work on any server with PHP support) 
PHP 4.3.x or high


Installation:
=============
Please take 5 minutes time and read installation instructions carefully and
completely! This will ensure a proper and easy installation.
a) Unzip the file.
b) Just include the code given in the "easter-calc.php" file into your webpage and place the file "sunday.php" in the same folder.
c) Set read, write permission to sunday.php (only for linux users).
d) Now call the "sunday.php" from your webpage after selecting the year for which you need the easter date.
e) Calculator that is simple and ease of use. 

